QualityReport¶

class quality_assessment.data_types.QualityReport(tape_id: str, test_type: quality_assessment.data_types.TestType, fail_information: Optional[list[quality_assessment.data_types.QualityParameterInfo]] = None)[source]¶
Class containing all information for a quality report for a tape

regarding a specific quality parameter.

tape_id (str): ID of the tested tape. test_type (TestType): Type of the test. fail_information (Optional[list[QualityParameterInfo]]): Information about failures passed (bool): Test passed or not.
